# Security Rules

DubForge is offline first.

Never introduce telemetry.

Never upload files.

Never collect analytics.

Escape filesystem paths.

Validate all user input.

Never execute shell commands with unsanitized values.

Use parameterized process execution.

Protect against path traversal.

Never expose stack traces in UI.

Show friendly errors.
